{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":580,"text":"I'm going to talk to you tonight"},{"time":2348,"text":"about coming out of the closet,"},{"time":4044,"text":"and not in the traditional sense,"},{"time":5256,"text":"not just the gay closet."},{"time":7568,"text":"I think we all have closets."},{"time":9622,"text":"Your closet may be telling someone"},{"time":11514,"text":"you love her for the first time,"},{"time":13736,"text":"or telling someone that you're pregnant,"},{"time":15882,"text":"or telling someone you have cancer,"},{"time":18414,"text":"or any of the other hard conversations"},{"time":20445,"text":"we have throughout our lives."},{"time":22711,"text":"All a closet is is a hard conversation,"},{"time":26381,"text":"and although our topics may vary tremendously,"},{"time":29435,"text":"the experience of being in"},{"time":31107,"text":"and coming out of the closet is universal."},{"time":34438,"text":"It is scary, and we hate it, and it needs to be done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40030,"text":"Several years ago,"},{"time":41399,"text":"I was working at the South Side Walnut Cafe,"},{"time":45170,"text":"a local diner in town,"},{"time":47241,"text":"and during my time there I would go through phases"},{"time":49956,"text":"of militant lesbian intensity:"},{"time":53521,"text":"not shaving my armpits,"},{"time":55296,"text":"quoting Ani DiFranco lyrics as gospel."},{"time":58845,"text":"And depending on the bagginess of my cargo shorts"},{"time":61100,"text":"and how recently I had shaved my head,"},{"time":63800,"text":"the question would often be sprung on me,"},{"time":65327,"text":"usually by a little kid:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":67410,"text":"\"Um, are you a boy or are you a girl?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":72577,"text":"And there would be an awkward silence at the table."},{"time":75249,"text":"I'd clench my jaw a little tighter,"},{"time":77672,"text":"hold my coffee pot with a little more vengeance."},{"time":80791,"text":"The dad would awkwardly shuffle his newspaper"},{"time":83628,"text":"and the mom would shoot a chilling stare at her kid."},{"time":85946,"text":"But I would say nothing,"},{"time":87650,"text":"and I would seethe inside."},{"time":89886,"text":"And it got to the point where every time I walked up"},{"time":91534,"text":"to a table that had a kid anywhere between\nthree and 10 years old, I was ready to fight."},{"time":95562,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":97008,"text":"And that is a terrible feeling."},{"time":99256,"text":"So I promised myself, the next\ntime, I would say something."},{"time":103104,"text":"I would have that hard conversation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105472,"text":"So within a matter of weeks, it happens again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108023,"text":"\"Are you a boy or are you a girl?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":110795,"text":"Familiar silence, but this time I'm ready,"},{"time":113948,"text":"and I am about to go all Women's Studies 101"},{"time":117899,"text":"on this table. (Laughter)"},{"time":120237,"text":"I've got my Betty Friedan quotes."},{"time":122737,"text":"I've got my Gloria Steinem quotes."},{"time":124535,"text":"I've even got this little bit from\n\"Vagina Monologues\" I'm going to do."},{"time":127833,"text":"So I take a deep breath and I look down"},{"time":131428,"text":"and staring back at me is a\nfour-year-old girl in a pink dress,"},{"time":135807,"text":"not a challenge to a feminist duel,"},{"time":137852,"text":"just a kid with a question:"},{"time":140412,"text":"\"Are you a boy or are you a girl?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":142783,"text":"So I take another deep breath,"},{"time":144428,"text":"squat down to next to her, and say,"},{"time":145795,"text":"\"Hey, I know it's kind of confusing."},{"time":147917,"text":"My hair is short like a boy's,"},{"time":149679,"text":"and I wear boy's clothes, but I'm a girl,"},{"time":151711,"text":"and you know how sometimes\nyou like to wear a pink dress,"},{"time":153678,"text":"and sometimes you like to\nwear your comfy jammies?"},{"time":156334,"text":"Well, I'm more of a comfy jammies kind of girl.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":160026,"text":"And this kid looks me dead in the eye,"},{"time":162114,"text":"without missing a beat, and says,"},{"time":163745,"text":"\"My favorite pajamas are purple with fish."},{"time":165697,"text":"Can I get a pancake, please?\""},{"time":167588,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":170309,"text":"And that was it. Just, \"Oh, okay. You're a girl."},{"time":173775,"text":"How about that pancake?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":176018,"text":"It was the easiest hard conversation"},{"time":178500,"text":"I have ever had."},{"time":180892,"text":"And why? Because Pancake Girl and I,"},{"time":183554,"text":"we were both real with each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186915,"text":"So like many of us,"},{"time":188691,"text":"I've lived in a few closets in my life, and yeah,"},{"time":191028,"text":"most often, my walls happened to be rainbow."},{"time":193642,"text":"But inside, in the dark,"},{"time":195666,"text":"you can't tell what color the walls are."},{"time":197834,"text":"You just know what it feels like to live in a closet."},{"time":201244,"text":"So really, my closet is no different than yours"},{"time":204995,"text":"or yours or yours."},{"time":207820,"text":"Sure, I'll give you 100 reasons"},{"time":209564,"text":"why coming out of my closet was\nharder than coming out of yours,"},{"time":211895,"text":"but here's the thing: Hard is not relative."},{"time":214097,"text":"Hard is hard."},{"time":216090,"text":"Who can tell me that explaining to\nsomeone you've just declared bankruptcy"},{"time":220233,"text":"is harder than telling someone\nyou just cheated on them?"},{"time":222472,"text":"Who can tell me that his coming out story"},{"time":225059,"text":"is harder than telling your five-year-old \nyou're getting a divorce?"},{"time":227936,"text":"There is no harder, there is just hard."},{"time":231275,"text":"We need to stop ranking our hard\nagainst everyone else's hard"},{"time":234813,"text":"to make us feel better or worse about our closets"},{"time":237212,"text":"and just commiserate on the \nfact that we all have hard."},{"time":241275,"text":"At some point in our lives, we all live in closets,"},{"time":244611,"text":"and they may feel safe,"},{"time":246541,"text":"or at least safer than what lies\non the other side of that door."},{"time":249488,"text":"But I am here to tell you,"},{"time":251253,"text":"no matter what your walls are made of,"},{"time":253378,"text":"a closet is no place for a person to live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":257946,"text":"Thanks. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":260106,"text":"So imagine yourself 20 years ago."},{"time":264334,"text":"Me, I had a ponytail, a strapless dress,"},{"time":269142,"text":"and high-heeled shoes."},{"time":271100,"text":"I was not the militant lesbian"},{"time":272995,"text":"ready to fight any four-year-old\nthat walked into the cafe."},{"time":276934,"text":"I was frozen by fear, curled up in the corner"},{"time":280623,"text":"of my pitch-black closet"},{"time":282887,"text":"clutching my gay grenade,"},{"time":285142,"text":"and moving one muscle is the scariest thing"},{"time":288774,"text":"I have ever done."},{"time":291087,"text":"My family, my friends, complete strangers --"},{"time":293303,"text":"I had spent my entire life"},{"time":294745,"text":"trying to not disappoint these people,"},{"time":296369,"text":"and now I was turning the world upside down"},{"time":299985,"text":"on purpose."},{"time":301609,"text":"I was burning the pages of the script"},{"time":303727,"text":"we had all followed for so long,"},{"time":305954,"text":"but if you do not throw that grenade, it will kill you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309597,"text":"One of my most memorable grenade tosses"},{"time":311475,"text":"was at my sister's wedding."},{"time":313636,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":315546,"text":"It was the first time that many in attendance"},{"time":318241,"text":"knew I was gay, so in doing \nmy maid of honor duties,"},{"time":321412,"text":"in my black dress and heels,"},{"time":323528,"text":"I walked around to tables"},{"time":325333,"text":"and finally landed on a table of my parents' friends,"},{"time":327502,"text":"folks that had known me for years."},{"time":330670,"text":"And after a little small talk,\none of the women shouted out,"},{"time":333781,"text":"\"I love Nathan Lane!\""},{"time":336283,"text":"And the battle of gay relatability had begun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":339371,"text":"\"Ash, have you ever been to the Castro?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":341218,"text":"\"Well, yeah, actually, we have\nfriends in San Francisco.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":343850,"text":"\"Well, we've never been there\nbut we've heard it's fabulous.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":346385,"text":"\"Ash, do you know my hairdresser Antonio?"},{"time":348246,"text":"He's really good and he has\nnever talked about a girlfriend.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":351395,"text":"\"Ash, what's your favorite TV show?"},{"time":353033,"text":"Our favorite TV show? Favorite: Will &amp; Grace."},{"time":355168,"text":"And you know who we love? Jack."},{"time":356771,"text":"Jack is our favorite.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":358596,"text":"And then one woman, stumped"},{"time":361188,"text":"but wanting so desperately to show her support,"},{"time":363676,"text":"to let me know she was on my side,"},{"time":366050,"text":"she finally blurted out,"},{"time":367930,"text":"\"Well, sometimes my husband wears pink shirts.\""},{"time":371276,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":373839,"text":"And I had a choice in that moment,"},{"time":375918,"text":"as all grenade throwers do."},{"time":377846,"text":"I could go back to my girlfriend\nand my gay-loving table"},{"time":381286,"text":"and mock their responses,"},{"time":383185,"text":"chastise their unworldliness and their inability"},{"time":385559,"text":"to jump through the politically correct \ngay hoops I had brought with me,"},{"time":388477,"text":"or I could empathize with them"},{"time":391345,"text":"and realize that that was maybe one of\nthe hardest things they had ever done,"},{"time":395062,"text":"that starting and having that conversation"},{"time":398458,"text":"was them coming out of their closets."},{"time":400843,"text":"Sure, it would have been easy\nto point out where they felt short."},{"time":404111,"text":"It's a lot harder to meet them where they are"},{"time":406366,"text":"and acknowledge the fact that they were trying."},{"time":408658,"text":"And what else can you ask someone to do but try?"},{"time":413503,"text":"If you're going to be real with someone,"},{"time":415576,"text":"you gotta be ready for real in return."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419146,"text":"So hard conversations are still not my strong suit."},{"time":422545,"text":"Ask anybody I have ever dated."},{"time":424566,"text":"But I'm getting better, and I follow what I like to call"},{"time":427794,"text":"the three Pancake Girl principles."},{"time":429431,"text":"Now, please view this through gay-colored lenses,"},{"time":433203,"text":"but know what it takes to come out of any closet"},{"time":436379,"text":"is essentially the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438338,"text":"Number one: Be authentic."},{"time":441018,"text":"Take the armor off. Be yourself."},{"time":442732,"text":"That kid in the cafe had no armor,"},{"time":444468,"text":"but I was ready for battle."},{"time":446764,"text":"If you want someone to be real with you,"},{"time":449353,"text":"they need to know that you bleed too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":452337,"text":"Number two: Be direct. Just\nsay it. Rip the Band-Aid off."},{"time":455347,"text":"If you know you are gay, just say it."},{"time":458083,"text":"If you tell your parents you might be gay,"},{"time":459951,"text":"they will hold out hope that this will change."},{"time":461593,"text":"Do not give them that sense of false hope."},{"time":464502,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":466455,"text":"And number three, and most important --"},{"time":471062,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":473386,"text":"Be unapologetic."},{"time":477117,"text":"You are speaking your truth."},{"time":479182,"text":"Never apologize for that."},{"time":483079,"text":"And some folks may have gotten hurt along the way,"},{"time":485501,"text":"so sure, apologize for what you've done,"},{"time":488439,"text":"but never apologize for who you are."},{"time":491943,"text":"And yeah, some folks may be disappointed,"},{"time":494687,"text":"but that is on them, not on you."},{"time":497447,"text":"Those are their expectations\nof who you are, not yours."},{"time":499919,"text":"That is their story, not yours."},{"time":504140,"text":"The only story that matters"},{"time":505926,"text":"is the one that you want to write."},{"time":508642,"text":"So the next time you find yourself"},{"time":510485,"text":"in a pitch-black closet clutching your grenade,"},{"time":512705,"text":"know we have all been there before."},{"time":516027,"text":"And you may feel so very alone, but you are not."},{"time":519205,"text":"And we know it's hard but we need you out here,"},{"time":522923,"text":"no matter what your walls are made of,"},{"time":525604,"text":"because I guarantee you there are others"},{"time":527618,"text":"peering through the keyholes of their closets"},{"time":529545,"text":"looking for the next brave soul to\nbust a door open, so be that person"},{"time":533677,"text":"and show the world that we\nare bigger than our closets"},{"time":536707,"text":"and that a closet is no place for a person"},{"time":540099,"text":"to truly live."}]},{"cues":[{"time":541839,"text":"Thank you, Boulder. Enjoy your night. (Applause)"}]}]}